{"id": "vos020", "name": "Audio_13St52_702_12_29", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Wind"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen A"], "content": "Let us in! Didn't you hear the announcment? This is the only place that's safe from the virus!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen B"], "content": "Why do you have to confiscate my device? How am I supposed to contact my family?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer A"], "content": "\"Electrical appliances that possess the function to connect to the internet system are Grade 1 restricted items in this Node.\" What a joke... Weren't you forced to flee here specifically because of technology?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer B"], "content": "You and your \"convenient\" technology, always looking down on Node 13... Now that s*** hit the fan, you're all crowding in here. You should be thanking us that we're not kicking you to the curb!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen A"], "content": "What'd you say?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer B"], "content": "You heard me! If this place had a weather system, would you still come here? We ain't got no more room!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen B"], "content": "Get outta my way! I'm getting in!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "Punches"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer B"], "content": "Oof! ... So now you're getting violent!?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer A"], "content": "You alright?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer B"], "content": "Ugh! Rotten tech addicts!\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "Punches"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["People_panic", "Crowd in chaos"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Resident"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">WAAHH!! Fight!!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "What's going on?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer C"], "content": "Sasha! Those people from other Nodes are fighting with the volunteers 'cuz they can't get in! The shelters got filled up a long time ago!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "Let me take a look.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_fast", "Hurried Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "Hey, quit fighting! Is now really the time to fight?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer B"], "content": "Don't try to stop me! We already made an exception for all those people. If we don't draw the line somewhere, we're gonna get in big trouble! I hate these foreigners!\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "Aigh... I'm a foreigner...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer B"], "content": "Uh, Sasha, you know that's not what I meant...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "Calm down yet?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer A"], "content": "Sasha, you're doing medical work at the shelter, you know we can't take in anymore people.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen A"], "content": "... <i>*sob*</i>... Please, please let us in, we'll give you our devices, we don't care. I don't want to die...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen B"], "content": "I'm so sorry, I'm just so anxious! You're a foreigner, you know how it feels to be rejected!\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "Oh...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer A"], "content": "Sasha, I know this is hard for you, but we really can't...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "Kneels"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "What... what are you doing?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen A"], "content": "Please, I really don't want to die...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen B"], "content": "Help us...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "... I've still got some rooms in my house. If we can...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer A"], "content": "No.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "Why!?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer A"], "content": "Look behind them... There's a whole line... Even if we take in two people, what are we supposed to do with the rest of them? We don't have an infinite number of rooms...\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen B"], "content": "Damn! She just promised, why stop her!?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Citizen A"], "content": "You're all colder than the Architects! Bastards!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "Punches"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer B"], "content": "Oof! Again!? I knew we shouldn't have let you in!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["People_panic", "Crowd in chaos"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Volunteer C"], "content": "Sasha, you'd better go. They'll take care of it... There's already nothing we can do.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "Yeah...\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...... R, is this the nightmare you spoke of...?</font>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Wind"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "中に入れてくれ！\nアナウンスを聞いただろ？\nここが唯一安全な場所なんだよ！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "なんで通信デバイスを没収するんだよ？\nこれじゃ家族と連絡ができないじゃないか。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア A"], "content": "「神経ネットワークに関する電子機器は、本Nodeでは第一級制限対象である」\n笑わせるな。お前たちはそのテクノロジーのせいでここまで追い込まれたんじゃないのか？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア B"], "content": "テクノロジーの便利な部分だけ利用して、普段はNode13は何もない場所だとバカにしているくせに……\n危機に追い込まれたらここに逃げこむだなんて……追い出されないだけマシだと思ってほしいね！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "なにを……！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア B"], "content": "その通りじゃないか！\nここが天気システムのようなバカげたものをまだ使っていたら、あんたたちはここに逃げてきたか？\nとにかくもう満員なんだ！これ以上は無理だと言ったら無理だ！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "どけ！中に入れろ！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "殴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア B"], "content": "がはっ……！\n……手まで出してくるのか……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア A"], "content": "大丈夫か？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア B"], "content": "っぐ……！\nこの……テクノロジー中毒者が！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "殴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["People_panic", "騒動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["住民"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">うわああ！ケンカだ！</font>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "何事だ？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア C"], "content": "Sasha！\n他のNodeから来たやつらが中に入れてもらえないからって、ボランティアに手を出したんだ！\nここの避難所はもう満員だって言ってるのに！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "アタシが行ってくる。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_fast", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "ちょっと！\n今はケンカなんてしてる場合じゃない。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア B"], "content": "止めるな！\nこれだけの人数を収容してる時点で異例なんだ！\n感謝されるならまだしも罵られるいわれはない！\nだから外の人間は嫌いなんだ！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "あちゃー、アタシも外の人間なんだけどね……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア B"], "content": "いや……あ……Sasha、違うんだ。\nそういう意味じゃない……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "落ち着いた？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア A"], "content": "Sasha、お前だって避難所で医療ボランティアをやってるんだ。\nここにはもうこれ以上収容できないことはわかってるだろ？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "ううう……お願いだ……入れてくれ……\nデバイスでも何でも渡すから……\n俺はまだ死にたくない……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "悪かった……俺が悪かった！\nあんたも外から来たんだろ？\n拒絶される苦痛もあんたならわかってくれるはずだ！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "う……っ\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア A"], "content": "Sasha、お前の気持ちも分かる。\nでも本当に……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "跪く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "何を……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "お願いします……\n本当に、死にたくないんです……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "お願いします……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "……アタシのところにまだ部屋が余ってる。\nそこなら……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア A"], "content": "ダメだ。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "なんで！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア A"], "content": "見ろ。\nこの二人の後ろにもまだまだ人が並んでる……\nこの二人を受け入れたところで残りの人たちはどうするつもりだ？\n無限に受け入れられるわけじゃない……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "彼女がいいって言ってんだ！\nなんで止めるんだよ！\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "血も涙もないやつらだ！くそが！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "殴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア B"], "content": "ぐあ！\nくそ……やっぱりお前らなんて受け入れなくて正解だった！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["People_panic", "騒動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ボランティア C"], "content": "Sasha、行こう。\nあとはあいつらがなんとかするよ。\n……もう俺たちにできることはない。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "うん……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……これが「悪夢」かな……ねぇ、R？</font>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Wind"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "讓我們進去！你們有聽到廣播吧？這裡是唯一不會被毒死的地方了！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "為什麼要沒收通訊裝置？這樣我怎麼和家人聯絡？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 A"], "content": "「具備導入網路系統功能的電子器具，在本 Node 列為一級管制品」，真可笑，你們不就是因為被科技逼到逃來這？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 B"], "content": "平常享用科技的方便，把 Node 13 嫌得一無是處……現在出事了全往這裡擠，沒把你們趕出去就不錯了！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "你說什麼！？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 B"], "content": "本來就是！要不是這裡早就不依賴天氣系統那種東西，你們這些傢伙還會逃過來嗎？就說已經沒辦法再塞了！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "滾開！我要進去！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 B"], "content": "嗚啊！……還真的打？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 A"], "content": "你沒事吧？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 B"], "content": "唔！你們這些科技成癮者！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["People_panic", "人群騷動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">哇啊啊！打起來了！</font>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "發生什麼事了？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 C"], "content": "Sasha！那幾位別的 Node 的人因為沒辦法進來，就和其他義工大打出手！這裡設置的避難處所早就滿了！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "我去看看。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_fast", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "喂，別再打了！現在是打架的時候嗎？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 B"], "content": "不要阻止我！已經破例讓那麼多人進來了，還要被罵？莫名其妙！所以我才討厭外地人！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "哎呀，我也是外地人呢……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 B"], "content": "呃，Sasha，妳知道我不是這個意思……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "冷靜下來了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 A"], "content": "Sasha，妳自己也在避難處所做醫護工作，應該很清楚不可能再收人了。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "嗚嗚……拜託讓我們進去吧，裝置什麼的都可以給你們。我還不想死啊……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "對不起，是我太著急了！妳也是外地人，應該能明白被拒絕的痛苦吧？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 A"], "content": "Sasha，我們知道妳很為難，但真的……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "跪地"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "你們……在做什麼？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "拜託了，我真的不想死啊……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "求求你們……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "……我那裡還有幾間客房，如果這樣的話……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 A"], "content": "不行。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "為什麼！？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 A"], "content": "你看他們後面，還排了一大堆……就算收了這兩人，剩下的妳該怎麼辦？我們可不是無限旅館啊……\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "可惡！她明明就答應了，為什麼還要阻止！\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "你們簡直比無人機還冷血！混蛋！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 B"], "content": "嗚啊！王○蛋……果然不讓你們進來是對的！\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["People_panic", "人群騷動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 C"], "content": "Sasha，先走吧，他們會處理好的。\n……我們已經幫不上忙了。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……這就是「噩夢」嗎……R？</font>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Wind"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 A"], "content": "들어가게 해줘! 방송 들었을 거 아니야? 안전한 곳은 여기가 유일하다고!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 B"], "content": "왜 통신 디바이스를 몰수하는 거야? 이러면 가족들이랑 연락할 방법이 없잖아?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 A"], "content": "「본 Node에서 네트워크 접속 기능이 있는 모든 전자 기기는 반입 금지이자 1급 제한 대상]이다. 웃기는군. 너희들은 그 기술 때문에 이런 신세가 된 거 아닌가?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 B"], "content": "평소엔 그 기술의 편리한 부분만을 사용하면서 Node 13을 무시했을 땐 언제고... 지금 쫓아내지 않는 것만으로도 다행으로 여기라고!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 A"], "content": "뭐라고...!?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 B"], "content": "말한대로다! 애초에 이곳에 기후 시스템과 같은 바보같은 것들이 존재했다면, 애초에 너희 같은 녀석들은 이곳으로 도망쳐오지도 않았겠지!! 그리고 그런 녀석들 때문에 이곳은 이미 만원이라고!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 B"], "content": "비켜! 난 들어갈 거야!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "주먹을 날린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 B"], "content": "으악! ......\n진짜로 폭력을 행사하다니? \n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 A"], "content": "괜찮아?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 B"], "content": "크윽...!\n과학 기술에 중독된 유기물 덩어리 주제에!\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "주먹을 날린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["People_panic", "군중 소란"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["주민"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">으아아아! 싸움이 일어났다!</font>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "무슨 일이지?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 C"], "content": "Sasha! \n다른 Node에서 온 사람 몇 명이 들어오지 못한다고 하니까 갑자기 직원들을 때리기 시작했어!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "내가 가서 볼게.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_fast", "다급한 발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "저기, 그만들 하지?\n지금 싸울 때가 아니잖아?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 B"], "content": "말리지 마! 지금 이 정도 인원까지 수용한 것도 이례적인 일이라고! 감사해해도 모자랄 판에 저 난리를 떨어!? 이래서 난 외지놈들이 싫어!\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "이런... 나도 외지인인데...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 B"], "content": "아... Sasha, 그런 뜻으로 한 말이 아니라...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "조금 진정됐어?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 A"], "content": "Sasha, 너도 피난소에서 의료 업무를 담당하고 있으니까 알 거 아니야. 더 이상의 인원 수용은 불가능하다는걸.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 A"], "content": "흑흑......제발 들여보내줘. 디바이스든 뭐든 줄 테니까 ... 죽고 싶지 않아...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 B"], "content": "미안해. 내가 잘못했어! 하지만 너도 외지인이라면 거절당하는 그 기분을 잘 알 거 아니야!\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "이런......\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 A"], "content": "Sasha, 네 기분 이해하지만, 지금 진짜 상황이...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "무릎을 꿇는다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "당신들......지금 무슨...?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 A"], "content": "부탁드립니다! \n정말로 죽고 싶지 않아요...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 B"], "content": "이렇게 빌게요......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "......내 쪽에 방 몇 개가 아직 남아있긴 한데, 거기라면...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 A"], "content": "안 돼.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "어째서!?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 A"], "content": "저 사람들 뒤에 줄을 선 사람들으 보라고.\n만약 이 두 명을 받아줬다간... 그 뒤에 있는 사람들은 어떻게 할 건데? 여긴 언제나 사람들을 받아주는 그런 여관이 아니라고....\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 B"], "content": "제길! 저 여자가 괜찮다고 하는데 네가 왜 껴드는 거야!\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["시민 A"], "content": "드론들보다 너희들이 더 나빠! 피도 눈물도 없는 놈들!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "주먹을 날린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 B"], "content": "크악! \nx새끼가......역시 너희 같은 녀석들은 절대로 받아주어선 안 돼!\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["People_panic", "군중 소란"], "content": ""}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["자원봉사자 C"], "content": "Sasha, 먼저 가.\n나머지는 지들이 알아서 하겠지.\n...여기서 우리가 할 수 있는 일은 없어.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "응......\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">......이것이 [악몽]...이란 걸까......R? </font>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 변경]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Wind"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "讓我們進去！你們有聽到廣播吧？這裡是唯一不會被毒死的地方了！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "為什麼要沒收通訊裝置？這樣我怎麼和家人聯絡？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 A"], "content": "「具備導入網路系統功能的電子器具，在本 Node 列為一級管制品」，真可笑，你們不就是因為被科技逼到逃來這？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 B"], "content": "平常享用科技的方便，把 Node 13 嫌得一無是處……現在出事了全往這裡擠，沒把你們趕出去就不錯了！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 A"], "content": "你說什麼！？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 B"], "content": "本來就是！要不是這裡早就不依賴天氣系統那種東西，你們這些傢伙還會逃過來嗎？就說已經沒辦法再塞了！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["市民 B"], "content": "滾開！我要進去！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 B"], "content": "嗚啊！……還真的打？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 A"], "content": "你沒事吧？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 B"], "content": "唔！你們這些科技成癮者！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["People_panic", "人群騷動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["居民"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">哇啊啊！打起來了！</font>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "發生什麼事了？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 C"], "content": "Sasha！那幾位別的 Node 的人因為沒辦法進來，就和其他義工大打出手！這裡設置的避難處所早就滿了！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "我去看看。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_fast", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "喂，別再打了！現在是打架的時候嗎？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 B"], "content": "不要阻止我！已經破例讓那麼多人進來了，還要被罵？莫名其妙！所以我才討厭外地人！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Sasha"], "content": "哎呀，我也是外地人呢……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["義工 B"], "content": "呃，Sasha，妳知道我不是這個意思……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "con